      <p>Finding a private tutor has always proved to be a challenging affair. But not anymore, thanks to Contut. All you have to do to a find the perfect tutor is to sign up with us and then choose from our wide database of private tutors. Find the perfect tutor based on location, subjects taugt, grades taught, ratings and price. Then all you have to do is send him/her a message from our platform and the two of you jointly come to an agreement. It's as easy as that.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="col-md-4">
      <h3 class="text-center text-uppercase">For Parents</h3>
