    </section>
    <section class="col-md-4">
      <h3 class="text-center text-uppercase">For Tutors</h3>
      <p>Teaching is a noble profession and of the most popular ones amongst young adults and university students. Howver finding students have always been a challenge and it has caused harm to both the students and the prospective tutors. With Contut, it's easier than ever before to become a tutor and acquire new students. All one has to do is to sign up with us and make a killer profile.</p>
